Data Analytics Project – From Excel to Power BI Dashboard

I transformed a raw sales dataset into an interactive Power BI dashboard. Here are the steps:

🔹 Step 1 – Data Preparation (Excel)
Worked with a transactional dataset containing fields like Invoice Date, Location, Country, Sales Manager, Customer Type, Product, Sales, Cost, and Profit.

🔹 Step 2 – Data Cleaning & Structuring
Organized and structured the dataset in Excel to ensure data consistency and readiness for analysis.

🔹 Step 3 – Data Visualization (Power BI)
Imported the dataset into Power BI and created an interactive dashboard to analyze key business metrics such as:

📊 Sales by Country
📊 Sales by Customer Type
📊 Product-wise Sales Performance
📊 Sales by Sales Manager
📊 Yearly Sales Trends
📊 Customer-wise Sales and Profit

📈 Key Business Metrics Identified
Total Sales: 89M
Total Cost: 40M
Total Profit: 49M



